|first1=Gregory A.
|last2=Ogburn
|first2=Joyce L.
|last3=Smith
|first3=J. Christina
|editor=Tony Stankus
|title=Journals of the century
|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=O-1qrN9FlYoC&pg=PA146
