|date=8 May 2002
|publisher=The Haworth Information Press
|location=Binghamton, NY.
|isbn=0-7890-1133-6
|pages=146–
|chapter=Journals of the Century in Anthropology and Archaeology}}</ref><ref name="Dyson1998">{{cite book
|author=Stephen L. Dyson
|title=Ancient marbles to American shores: classical archaeology in the United States
|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=JKerZDGqSWQC&pg=PA47
|accessdate=17 October 2011
|year=1998
|publisher=University of Pennsylvania Press
|isbn=0-8122-3446-4
|pages=47–49, 97, 104}}</ref> 1885年[[普林斯頓大學|普林斯頓大學]][[亞瑟·弗羅辛漢姆|亞瑟·弗羅辛漢姆]]和艾倫·馬昆德（Allan Marquand）加入與其合作。<ref name="Dyson1998"/> 前者成為該雜誌首任編輯，任職到1896年。<ref name="Dyson1998"/>

該雜誌主要領域在於[[歐洲|歐洲]]和[[地中海盆地|地中海]]的考古界動向，也包括[[近東|近東]]與[[埃及|埃及]]，其時間跨度則為[[史前|史前]]到[[古典時代晚期|古典時代晚期]]。<ref name="stankus"/> 也出版書評、博物館展品評論和死者名冊。每年在一、四、七和十月出版四期書面版和電子版。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ajaonline.org/subscribe|title=American Journal of Archaeology:Subscribe|accessdate=17 October 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ajaonline.org/society|title=The Society for the American Journal of Archaeology|accessdate=17 October 2011}}</ref>

